{
  "stem": "7860.2",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my German shepherd dog looked down at them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I said-- and my children are sitting in the car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know if they noticed or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I proceeded telling to my late wife, Helen, children who have no supervision get themselves in trouble.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They get themselves pregnant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then I proceeded to telling her about the newspaper adventure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I said, that's what I used to do with my mother-- rebel because there was no father at home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You see, there's no father here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She will come home pregnant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "As I got through saying this, my older daughter Marcia says to me, Daddy, I promise I won't do it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Please tell me how it's done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told my wife, who was very educated, I said, you handle it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to child guidance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You tell them to take off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, you started something, you finish it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are fighting amongst each other who is going to handle such a thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't ask no question, neither did the dog.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just Marcia was so inquisitive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Daddy, I promise I won't do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, if you do it, I'll kill you, because you know what do I think I survived the war for.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she kept saying, Daddy, I promise I won't do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's all I want know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "How did the flame come out the paper?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you see, in a child's mind is different than an adult.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We see it differently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You're asking about me being afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's you taking it with the punches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You were just a small boy, and you were all alone during that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Weren't you feeling lonely?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to play cards with one hand-- the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
